    "# 👨🏽‍🤝‍👨🏿👩🏼‍🤝‍👨🏾👩🏼‍🤝‍👩🏻<br>Groupwork!\n",
    "\n",
    "## RGB Activity (Pt. I)\n",
    "<hr>\n",
    "\n",
    ":::{.gray-container .fourtyeightpt-font}\n",
    "**Materials Needed:**\n",
