    ":::\n",
    "<br>\n",
    "\n",
    "## Activity (Pt. II) — Instructions\n",
    "<hr>\n",
    "\n",
    ":::{.fourtyeightpt-font}\n",
    "1. Using the round stickies and graph paper, create a scatterplot.\n",
    "2. Color values (R, G, or B — per your group) go on the **x-axis**.\n",
    "3. Nitrate concentrations go on the **y-axis**.\n",
