    "\n",
    "# 💻 Activity — Pt. III:<br>Regression Modeling\n",
    "\n",
    "## Regression Modeling\n",
    "<hr>\n",
    "\n",
    "```{=html}\n",
    "<center>\n",
    "<div style=\"position: relative; padding-bottom: 56.25%; height: 0; overflow: hidden; max-width: 100%;\">\n",
    "  <iframe \n",
    "    src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/e18KM681cmg?start=8&end=74\" \n",
    "    frameborder=\"0\" \n",
    "    allowfullscreen\n",
    "    style=\"position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; border: 0;\">\n",
    "  </iframe>\n",
    "</div>\n",
    "</center>\n",
    "```"
   ]
