    "## From Regression to Equation\n",
    "<hr>\n",
    "\n",
    ":::{.activity-text}\n",
    "The linear regression produces the equation for the **line of best fit**.  <br>\n",
    ":::\n",
    "\n",
    ":::{.fourtyeightpt-font}\n",
    "Remember ***y = mx + b***? We can just substitute!\n",
    ":::\n",
    "\n",
    ":::{.dkorange-container .thirtyfourpt-font}\n",
    "Click ▶️ **Run Code** to see the slope-intercept equation.\n",
    ":::\n",
    "\n",
    "```python\n",
    "print(f\"y = {slope:.2f}x + {intercept:.2f}\")\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "## From Regression to Equation\n",
